{"tid":2409001,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[民運份子行動派入]請將支共派解放軍去緬甸既事推到最高","createTime":"2021-02-15T12:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T12:51:10.000Z","uid":19557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a20d6e6da32719f9ac3e4eab32ce9cf6f6fd34a3","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"第177日 ｜緬甸軍隊政變 中共日日空運海鮮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2408777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2408777</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n搵你地既方法聯絡當地社運前線 將呢d 事講比佢地知 <br />\n叫佢地唔好咁天真 支共唔係善男信女 唔會聽你地好言好語勸到 <br />\n依家支共仲派埋解放軍同武器黎扮緬甸軍想重演一次64天安門事件<br />\n我勸緬甸人一定要搵多d 證據證明有解放軍扮緬甸軍<br />\n最好就係捉佢幾個解放軍 迫供佢 <br />\n當件事去到有證有據支共介入人地國家既時候 好多野其他國家都可以出師有名 打柒支共 唔單止緬甸既事 仲可以燒埋維吾爾族種族滅絕 更加可以燒到香港既事 所以呢單野不單可以幫緬甸 仲可以幫埋自己"},{"pid":"1297dc5acf0bf3088fbc7ca68e5e8ad6d5860302","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc55fad70df4a2af3d4be8e8ae9d5cc7bcb12011","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54873004b64e3578fe7a2053101fc35744c2c9e1","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb980e7be230569ae17934e12b8ba5c6c0dbd801","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4af1be933e8a9924cf0dc77cf90fa27359fdd0e","tid":2409001,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5c75fe5f9829b312535d26688624309ce287f9","tid":2409001,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}